April 18 Bitcoin ( Update ) BTC price dumped after breaking major support 60k - 58k .. we try to find actual reason of this heavy dump , as of now it looks like the dump is because of Margin Trading .. We all know that big players / whales are using bot / algo System on Margin trading .. when btc break support bots start to cut their longs which cause panic selling .. We will share full report on this soon .. as of now btc broke all support and touch 50k , price bounce back as relief rally but still its below 50 Day moving average which was working as big support from long time .. Now all eyes on today's closing candle . If BTC able to finish today'scandle above 56400 than it will give confidence to market , otherwise we will retest 50k again ... Correction is part of bull run , we saw many such a big correction in 2017 bull rally and also we saw such correction near 10 Jan and 22 Feb .. Share this with others ✅
